import React from 'react'
import Counter from '../Components/Counter'
import { Row, Col, Container } from 'react-bootstrap'
import Navigation from '../Components/Navigation'

const Widgetscreen = () => {
  return (
    <Container>
      <Navigation />
      <Row>
        <Col>
          <Counter />
        </Col>
      </Row>
    </Container>
  )
}

export default Widgetscreen
